{"tid":1204410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［求解夢］夢見馬路大擠塞，係咩意思","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:13:56.000Z","uid":64831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b196b2d19f3bd337a405f33981af82f159c1a7f1","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"頭先發夢夢見：<br />\n凌晨時份，好多小朋友喺Y城各個主要幹道路面倒食用油<br />\n天光之後，全城擠塞<br />\n好恐怖，係咪我份新工太大壓力？"},{"pid":"41199e7545ba7eaddd0bebe7d0395dc0da10346d","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"［本報訊］石硤尾龍翔道昨午二時許發生漏油事件，長達二十米油迹遺留西行中線，警員需封鎖三條行車線由工人鋪上木糠「吸油」。警員在路旁撿獲一個壓至變形食油鐵罐，疑是罪魁禍首。事件擾攘一個半小時，工人趕及在下班時間前洗淨馬路，其間警方封閉龍翔道西行三條行車線，車龍延伸一公里。警方估計有運送食油貨車駛經上址，其中一罐食油跌下馬路遭車輛輾爆導致食油四溢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060316/5740722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060316%2F5740722&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=589aa143\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20060316%2F5740722&h=03d6771a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20060316/5740722</a><br />\n<br />\n搵到新聞報導，幫唔幫到我解夢"},{"pid":"a1d43b03925f19d468c3c959994513465608dc54","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"心急人上"},{"pid":"16c4bcc49d76b66d982e151dd8047b38e9775d36","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421893b5ce30cfb83a329057bb400b04d7969679","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:07:35.000Z","msg":"help"},{"pid":"4072448e733a85a7083f593cc6586604c7a0a6e1","tid":1204410,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dis